$ Powershell module WinConfig add-dirToPath
@ add-dirToPath

`add-dirToPath` adds a director to user's or machine's `PATH` or `PSModulePath` environment variable.

code {
add-dirToPath $pwd
add-dirToPath $pwd -machine
add-dirToPath $pwd -psModulePath
code }

sa:
  This function is found in the PowerShell module â†’ Windows/PowerShell/modules/personal/WinConfig.
